window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>EARTH FACES ITS GREATEST THREAT YET.</p> <p><b>A catastrophic accident</b> at one of the ancient alien portals unleashes a deadly contagion across multiple inhabited worlds.</p> <p>Time is running out, and it's up to a courageous team of explorers, soldiers, and scientists, all familiar faces from previous adventures, to embark on a perilous intergalactic mission.</p> <p>Through the enigmatic portals, they will journey to distant alien worlds, each with its own unique dangers and challenges, in a desperate race to avert disaster.</p> <p>Told through gripping mission logs, <i>Awakened</i> weaves a captivating tale of courage, sacrifice, and the unbreakable bonds that unite us, even across the vast expanse of the cosmos.</p> <p><b><i>Awakened is the thrilling fourth and final installment in the critically-acclaimed Saturn's Legacy series.</i></b></p>"; 
